event_detail.name: Prambanan Jazz Festival 2024 #SatuDekadeBersama

list: Enjoy a weekend to remember for jazz lovers at Prambanan Jazz 2024 #SatuDekadeBersama
Sing along with the star-studded lineup Maliq & D'Essentials, Kahitna, Tulus, and more to be announced
On 5, 6, and 7 July 2024, celebrate the magical moments against the stunning backdrop of the Prambanan temple
Grab your tickets now and make some beautiful memories at Prambanan Temple

locationInfo.summary: Pelataran Candi Prambanan, Jl. Raya Solo - Yogyakarta No.16, Kranggan, Bokoharjo, Kec. Prambanan, Kabupaten Sleman, Daerah Istimewa Yogyakarta 55571, Indonesia

children.htmlText: You don't need to make a reservation for your visit.

list: Show or scan the Traveloka voucher on your phone at the ticket booth to receive a wristband. Please adjust the brightness of your mobile phone screen before scanning the QR code on your voucher.

children.htmlText: *Redemption instructions may vary, depending on the voucher type you book.

list: Specific artist performance schedules may be informed prior to the event date, and may also be changed during the event due to unexpected weather or technical situation.
Please check your registered email regularly prior to the event date.

The promoter has the right to refuse entry to guests who are intoxicated, clearly affected by drugs or deemed unfit for entry. Any guests found in possession of illegal substances, weapons and/or other prohibited items will also be refused entry. Anyone found carrying these items will be reported to the police immediately. No refunds will be given.
Do not take any photos of your e-voucher and post them online to prevent unauthorized misuse, i.e. other parties copying and claiming your tickets.
Partner reserves the right to deny entry to visitors who are unable to show a valid ID.
Umbrellas, selfie sticks, cigarettes, matches, DSLR cameras, mirrorless cameras, drones, and fragile objects are prohibited inside the venue
Free admission policy available. Children below 5 years old may enter free of charge
Valid for multiple entries during visit
Wristband
No outside food and drinks are allowed

termsAndConditions.htmlText: *Terms & conditions may vary, depending on the voucher type you book.

experienceContent.htmlText: Immerse yourself in a weekend to be etched in the hearts of jazz enthusiasts at Prambanan Jazz 2024 #SatuDekadeBersama. Join in the harmonious melodies as you sing along with the illustrious lineup featuring Maliq & D'Essentials, Kahitna, Tulus, and other incredible artists yet to be revealed. From July 5th to 7th, 2024, revel in the magic of jazz against the breathtaking setting of the Prambanan temple!
